Coffee, rum, cigars, the Sierra Maestra, the Bay of Pigs and the Isle of Pines, the Tropicana Cabaret, the patron saint of Cuba, the Virgen de la Caridad del Cobre, Santería, African religion practiced by the descendants of those slaves, all of which could fill many pages.
