It's almost always worth a rule: when a star gets into a crisis region or minefields, then something like "Rangoon" with Patricia Arguette, "Across All Borders" with Angelina Jolie or "Blood Diamonds" with Leonardo DiCaprio appears.
Possibly all these conflicts occurred in a short space of time.
